# Day 1 - Project B: Node.js Dockerfile with Healthcheck

## 🧠 Objective
Containerize a Node.js app using a Dockerfile with proper healthcheck.

## 🛠️ Stack
- Node.js 18 (Alpine)
- Express.js
- Docker

## 🚀 How to Run
```bash
docker build -t node-docker-app .
docker run -d -p 3000:3000 node-docker-app

30-day-devops-challenge/
├── day01-docker-flask-app/
├── day01-docker-node-app/
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── index.js
│   │   └── package.json
│   ├── Dockerfile
│   └── README.md

# Go to project folder
cd day01-docker-node-app

# Build image
docker build -t node-docker-app .

# Run container
docker run -d -p 3000:3000 node-docker-app

